data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION! This house is a must see with unbelievable potential!   It is the perfect family home in sought after Johns Creek, with A rated Chet's Creek elementary within walking distance!  Must see backyard with a saltwater pool on one of the biggest preserve lots in the neighborhood. Cook's kitchen with solid surface counter tops with tile back splash in the kitchen with an island. Main living space has an open and airy floor plan w/ vaulted ceilings and tile and wood flooring throughout. . Separate office/den that could be utilized as a 4th bedroom. One of the best ''A'' rated schools in all of Duval county at the entrance to the community. Don't miss this home!
